tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE response_times (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  response_time INT,
  endpoint VARCHAR,
  status_code INT
)

CREATE TABLE customer_satisfaction (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  satisfaction_score INT,
  feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE reports (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  report_id INT,
  report_name VARCHAR,
  metric_type VARCHAR,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_metrics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dashboard_id INT,
  metric_name VARCHAR,
  metric_value FLOAT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  activity_type VARCHAR,
  activity_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  session_id INT
)
